      "comment": "WON'T BE LONG (1) put in a much better performance last start when in the placings at Q Straight behind Top The Lot (19.39) in a Grade 6. Has the early speed to land on the pace and can stick on. Some good form is emerging from his last run. Deserves serious consideration. BIG GRIN (5) had been racing well prior to his last start seventh at this track following a Maiden win three back with a second placing. Can find the frame this time. BORROWED LOVE (2) was prominent throughout when winning two back but could manage only midfield last time when 4th and beaten 2.5 lengths at this track (20.25). Should be about the mark. NOBLE TOBY (8) must be included in main hopes on latest effort.",
